item.description:
duplicate: <p>
Duplicate of <a class="new ticket" href="http://core.trac.wordpress.org/ticket/16557" title="#16557: enhancement: Ability to disable redirect_guess_404_permalink() (new)">#16557</a>. Try a workaround from there:
</p>
<pre class="wiki">function remove_redirect_guess_404_permalink( $redirect_url ) {
	if ( is_404() )
		return false;
	return $redirect_url;
}
add_filter( 'redirect_canonical', 'remove_redirect_guess_404_permalink' );
</pre>
